{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/BROKEN_MIND_GIF_Steam.gif?t=1721306330\" /><br><br>BROKEN MIND is an action Survival Horror. Investigate, solve the puzzles and find out what happened to Laura Campbell. If she is still alive you must act quickly!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WHAT HAPPENED TO LAURA CAMPBELL?</h2><br>In BROKEN MIND, you play Agent Frank Morgan, a detective with a dark past. You will have to investigate the disappearance of a teenage girl who was abducted during a live Internet broadcast. The investigation is accelerated when Laura's phone emits a signal a few miles away in the middle of the forest!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FIGHT FOR YOUR LIFE</h2><br>BROKEN MIND is a narrative game that requires you to fight. In the course of your investigation, you'll encounter numerous enemies who will try to stand in your way.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/BROKEN-MIND-Action.gif?t=1721306330\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SOLVE PUZZLES</h2><br>During your investigation, you'll come across a number of puzzles that you'll need to solve. Keep a close eye on your surroundings for clues.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/BROKEN-MIND-Puzzle.gif?t=1721306330\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">YOU'LL HAVE TO BE DISCRET</h2><br>Sometimes fighting isn't an option, so you'll have to hide to avoid being caught by your assailants.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/BROKEN-MIND-Game-Infiltration.gif?t=1721306330\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">UNIQUE HAND MADE DRAWINGS</h2><br>Discover a dark, oppressive atmosphere with graphics that blend 3D scenery and hand-drawn images.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/BROKEN-MIND-Game.gif?t=1721306330\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><br>- A narrative game with gameplay that mixes investigations, puzzles and combat!<br>- Follow the story from different angles, playing several characters with unique skills.<br>- Fully voice acted game thanks to 7 actors.<br>- An oppressive atmosphere, with a graphic style mixing 3D and hand made drawings<br>- The biggest project of the studio !<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/BROKEN-MIND-Rating.jpg?t=1721306330\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"CHAPTER I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559950/69455d18b67020e30a5bd6cf0054957dd621243a.jpg"},{"name":"CHAPTER II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559950/2cc083afd66433016486b0c6e72635b5ca78b143.jpg"},{"name":"CHAPTER III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559950/5c3f2282895891e823b451769ecf8d452819b066.jpg"},{"name":"CHAPTER IV","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559950/8242bfb4f1691eda9c5cf674117fe6bb0eca8206.jpg"},{"name":"CHAPTER V","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559950/be41dda2e12268efba9a1744c528757b9bca7383.jpg"},{"name":"CHAPTER VI","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559950/a66687cbf37d624ee4071b54071bb4c5b9f89606.jpg"},{"name":"CHAPTER VII","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559950/8644fe03ca77421b0a8c26045ad3fb86fb4e4b5c.jpg"},{"name":"CHAPTER VIII","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559950/aea44297ab9f0254c63148f4e6ac5f3c8ccdc985.jpg"},{"name":"CHAPTER IX","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559950/16c34d6f910df8a8e66f988b6bd5249aa4677dc5.